Class JGMPVelocity

java.lang.Object
com.boole.jgmp.physics.JGMPVelocity
public class JGMPVelocity extends Object
Kinematics Velocity Physics Model for the JGMP Library.
Includes Vector Math and 2D Kinematics calculations.
